title: [Orcswold, Fields]
description: A cool wind sweeps over the grassy field, murmuring in the grass and chilling the air with a touch of mist from the high moors to the east.  Startled by your presence, a sleek brown rabbit leaps from behind a stone and bounds away into the grass.

A cool night wind sweeps over the grassy field, murmuring in the grass and chilling the air with a touch of mist from the high moors to the east.  Startled by your presence, a sleek brown rabbit leaps from behind a stone and bounds away into the grass.
